body.name: X99 LGA2011-3 DDR4 Motherboard, Computer Desktop Motherboard Gaming Mainboard, Support 4 DDR4 2133/2400/2800, with 8 SATA2.0 Port & 1 SSD M.2 Interface
body.stockDetail: Only 4 left in stock - order soon.
features: 【Power Adapter】This platform requires a powerful power supply. Make sure your power supply is enough to support this platform. (At least 500W brand power supply); The motherboard power connector: 1x8 pin, 1x24pin.
【Memory】The computer motherboard supports 4 DDR4 2133/2400/2800 memory, the maximum support 32GB. Support ECC/REG/Non ECC memory. Follow the general memory allocation standards for desktop computers.
【Compatibility】When the motherboard is used for i7 series processors, please do not use REG ECC memory at the same time because the motherboard and REG ECC are not compatible with each other.

【High Quality Material】The computer motherboard is made of high quality PCB material, sturdy and durable. The packing list includes a motherboard baffle to protect the motherboard from jitter problems and extend the life of the motherboard.

【After-sales Service】We will undergo strict inspection before delivery and you can rest assured to buy and use. If you dissatisfied of our motherboard, please contact us at any time online, we will try our best to help you solve any problems.
